// ============================================================================
// MIGRATION NOTE — v3.0 Full Rebuild (2026-03-26)
// Old sheets: Hızlı Veri Girişi, Borç Takibi, Alacak Takibi, Nakit Akışı,
//             Dashboard, Aksiyon Merkezi, Ana Kontrol Paneli, Stok Yatırım Planı
// New sheets: Sabit Giderler, Stok Envanter, Stok Hareketleri, SKU Karlılık,
//             İthalat Planı, Talep ve Stok Baskısı, Risk Paneli
// Major upgrades:
//  - Full capital allocation & import timing decision engine
//  - Revenue capacity modeled as f(stock, turnover, stockout risk)
//  - Dynamic minimum cash reserve (not hardcoded)
//  - Multi-bucket 30/60/90 day cash projection
//  - SKU-level profitability, import scoring, stock intelligence
//  - Marketplace net payout modeling (commission, shipping, ads deductions)
//  - Fixed expense auto-generation into Borç Takibi
//  - Risk panel aggregating all business risks
//  - Actionable command-output Aksiyon Merkezi
// ============================================================================

